  INSTALL
    npm install -g @mariozechner/pi-coding-agent
    pi install https://github.com/jeonghyeon-net/pi

  UPDATE
    pi update

  EXTENSIONS
    claude-code-ui … Claude Code dark 기본 UI chrome + 도구 렌더링
    claude-hooks-bridge … `.claude/settings.json` hooks를 pi lifecycle event로 브리지
    mcp … MCP 서버 통합 (proxy tool, lazy connection, metadata caching)
    session-title … 첫 요청을 바탕으로 명료한 세션 이름/터미널 제목 자동 설정
    spinner … Claude Code source 기반 working spinner
    subagent … `@jeonghyeon.net/pi-subagents` 기반 subagent 실행/관리
    supervisor … `@jeonghyeon.net/pi-supervisor` 기반 목표 감시/steer
    tasks … `@jeonghyeon.net/pi-tasks` 기반 작업 추적
    web-access … `@jeonghyeon.net/pi-web-access` 기반 웹 검색/콘텐츠 수집

  SKILLS
    api-and-interface-design … Guides stable API and interface design
    browser-testing-with-devtools … Tests in real browsers
    ci-cd-and-automation … Automates CI/CD pipeline setup
    code-review-and-quality … Conducts multi-axis code review
    code-simplification … Simplifies code for clarity
    context-engineering … Optimizes agent context setup
    debugging-and-error-recovery … Guides systematic root-cause debugging
    deprecation-and-migration … Manages deprecation and migration
    documentation-and-adrs … Records decisions and documentation
    frontend-ui-engineering … Builds production-quality UIs
    git-workflow-and-versioning … Structures git workflow practices
    idea-refine … Refines ideas iteratively
    incremental-implementation … Delivers changes incrementally
    performance-optimization … Optimizes application performance
    planning-and-task-breakdown … Breaks work into ordered tasks
    security-and-hardening … Hardens code against vulnerabilities
    shipping-and-launch … Prepares production launches
    source-driven-development … Grounds every implementation decision in official documentation
    spec-driven-development … Creates specs before coding
    test-driven-development … Drives development with tests
    using-agent-skills … Discovers and invokes agent skills

  PROMPTS
    (none)

  THEMES
    claude-code-dark … Claude Code dark theme token 매핑

